    "body": "The `-o` flag is only supported with starship 1.14+. You can use `>` instead to redirect the output instead for now (`starship preset pure-preset > ~/.config/starship.toml`). Manjaro will hopefully provide an upgrade to starship soon. There is already an updated version in Manjaro testing and unstable.",
